        "username": "ajbeamon",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.foundationdb.org/ajbeamon/{size}/13_2.png",
        "created_at": "2019-08-10T13:52:19.492Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The function needs to serialize onto the network thread behind other previously run operations in order to count their effects, but it won\u2019t communicate at all with the cluster. It should return fairly quickly unless you are keeping the network thread very busy, in which case you\u2019ll be experiencing extra latency on all future returning operations.</p>",
